        "title": "<p>The Art Of Giving | Main Event</p>",
        "description": "<p>A fresh and eye catching main for a warm Christmas day. </p><p>In partnership with Australian chef <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sian_redgrave/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/sian_redgrave/\"><em><strong>Sian Redgrave</strong></em></a>, we’re excited to bring you the second edition of our festive menu, paired with our <a href=\"/collections/personalised-gift-guide\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"The Personalised Gift Guide\"><em><strong>Personalised Gift Guide</strong></em></a><em><strong>. </strong></em></p><p>It’s the most wonderful time of the year — so make it your own with gifts full of sentiment and story. From the subtle to the extravagant, designed to be personalised with birthstones, engravings and charms.</p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
        "button_1_text": "",
        "button_1_link": "",
        "button_style": "underline"
      }
